{"about_the_game":"<strong>Star Mountain</strong> is a fast paced 1v1 game where you must race to get a star before your opponent. Build your own platforms, and block your opponent to get to the star first!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Freeze Yourself to Reach New Heights</h2>The core mechanic of <strong>Star Mountain</strong> is the ability to build your own platforms, using you and your opponents characters to reach the star. By frequently <strong>freezing</strong> your character, you can be <strong>offensive</strong> to create your own path to victory, or <strong>defensive</strong> to block in your opponent.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2938920/extras/new_clip-2-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1725818137\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Online and Local Multiplayer</h2>Friends are across the world? Got no friends? No matter! <strong>Star mountain</strong> features <strong>online multiplayer</strong> so you can play with amazing strangers and maybe meet your new best friend! Or, if you're lucky and have friends, there is also <strong>local multiplayer</strong>! (With split keyboard and controller compatibility)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">As featured in Wonderville arcade in New York City!</h2>From March 1st - June 1st 2024, <strong>Star Mountain</strong> was featured in an arcade cabinet thanks to Mark Kleback and the team at <strong>Wonderville NYC</strong>!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2938920/extras/IMG_6981__1_.png?t=1725818137\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2938920/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1725818137","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2938920/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1725818137","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2938920/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1725818137","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamst